00:00:00.274 --> 00:00:02.127
Welcome to Jawbone customer care.

00:00:02.456 --> 00:00:05.269
In this video, we'll review the band's different modes.

00:00:05.391 --> 00:00:06.961
Let's get started!

00:00:07.156 --> 00:00:08.878
The band has four different modes:

00:00:09.113 --> 00:00:13.822
Awake Mode, Sleep Mode, Stopwatch Mode, and Power Nap Mode.

00:00:14.270 --> 00:00:16.015
Switching between modes is easy.

00:00:16.316 --> 00:00:18.763
Awake Mode is used to track steps throughout the day.

00:00:19.124 --> 00:00:21.104
This is the default mode of your band.

00:00:22.461 --> 00:00:25.109
Sleep Mode is used to track the quality and quantity

00:00:25.148 --> 00:00:26.829
of your light and sound sleep.

00:00:27.125 --> 00:00:29.750
To start Sleep Mode, press and hold the band button

00:00:29.758 --> 00:00:32.497
until the band vibrates and the moon symbol flashes.

00:00:32.892 --> 00:00:34.456
The color of the flash may vary,

00:00:34.476 --> 00:00:36.370
depending on the type of band you own.

00:00:36.870 --> 00:00:39.564
To return to Awake Mode, press and hold the band button.

00:00:40.026 --> 00:00:42.818
The band will vibrate and the sun symbol will flash once.

00:00:43.220 --> 00:00:45.415
Please note that you must return to Awake Mode

00:00:45.426 --> 00:00:47.215
before switching to other modes.

00:00:47.723 --> 00:00:49.626
Stopwatch Mode is used to track your steps


00:00:49.656 --> 00:00:51.379
during a specific period of time,

00:00:51.409 --> 00:00:53.284
or during a specific activity.

00:00:53.441 --> 00:00:56.197
For example, a basketball game or a dance class.

00:00:56.771 --> 00:00:59.595
To start Stopwatch Mode, press the band button twice,

00:00:59.639 --> 00:01:01.452
holding on the second press.

00:01:01.723 --> 00:01:04.293
When you start Stopwatch Mode, your band will vibrate

00:01:04.317 --> 00:01:06.527
and the sun symbol will flash three times.

00:01:07.468 --> 00:01:10.163
Power Nap Mode helps you calculate your optimal nap length

00:01:10.192 --> 00:01:12.337
and awakens you with gentle vibrations.

00:01:12.716 --> 00:01:15.679
To start Power Nap Mode, press the band button three times,

00:01:15.692 --> 00:01:17.521
holding on the last press.

00:01:17.660 --> 00:01:20.382
When you activate Power Nap Mode, your band will vibrate

00:01:20.402 --> 00:01:22.661
and the moon symbol will flash three times.

00:01:23.346 --> 00:01:25.225
If you aren't sure what mode your band is in,

00:01:25.260 --> 00:01:27.265
you can check by pressing your band button once.

00:01:27.654 --> 00:01:30.511
A band symbol will flash to indicate the current mode.

00:01:30.784 --> 00:01:33.671
If you have an UP 24, you can also check band mode

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:35.852
by opening the app on your phone or iPad.

00:01:36.226 --> 00:01:38.074
A band status symbol will be displayed

00:01:38.086 --> 00:01:40.209
in the upper right corner of your home screen.

00:01:40.587 --> 00:01:43.049
If your band is in Awake Mode, a band icon without

00:01:43.055 --> 00:01:44.736
a status symbol will appear.

00:01:45.128 --> 00:01:48.267
You can also use the UP app to switch between band modes.

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:51.478
Tap the band icon in the upper right corner of your home srceen

00:01:51.487 --> 00:01:52.974
to open the right menu.

00:01:53.076 --> 00:01:55.887
Simply tap the mode you'd like to turn on or off.

00:01:56.129 --> 00:01:58.511
Thanks for watching and enjoy living UP!

